ientist / ML Engineer (Priority 1):** Focus on model accuracy, data cleaning, and algorithm optimization.\n    - **Full-Stack Developer (Priority 1):** Focus on API development, database integration, and frontend implementation.\n    - **Project Manager / Operations Specialist (Priority 2):** Focus on sprint planning, scope management, cross-functional communication, and ensuring lean execution.'}, 'id': 'IoOowL39ctlQuoyErxC72e1mF3G97NHC', 'type': 'tool_call'}]
